sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as trainer-controller-manager<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant JobSet as JobSet Controller
    participant TrainPod as Training Pod (rank 0)<br/>28080/TCP HTTP
    participant MPIWorker as MPI Worker Pods<br/>2222/TCP SSH

    Note over User, MPIWorker: Flow 1: TrainJob Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl create TrainJob<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token/OIDC
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-trainer-...-trainjob<br/>HTTPS/9443, API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob created

    K8sAPI--)Controller: Watch event: TrainJob created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET TrainJob, TrainingRuntime<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Runtime spec resolved

    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE/PATCH JobSet<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE NetworkPolicy (RHAI)<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: UPDATE TrainJob/status<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token

    JobSet--)K8sAPI: Watch event: JobSet
    JobSet->>K8sAPI: CREATE Jobs/Pods

    Note over Controller, TrainPod: Flow 2: RHAI Progression Tracking

    loop Every reconciliation cycle
        Controller->>K8sAPI: LIST Pods (training job)<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod list with IPs
        Controller->>TrainPod: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/28080, plaintext, No auth
        TrainPod-->>Controller: Training metrics (JSON)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH TrainJob annotations<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    end

    Note over Controller, MPIWorker: Flow 3: MPI Distributed Training Setup

    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE Secret (SSH key pair)<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE ConfigMap (hostfile)<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    Note over TrainPod, MPIWorker: MPI launcher initiates distributed training
    TrainPod->>MPIWorker: SSH connection<br/>SSH/2222, RSA key pair auth
    MPIWorker-->>TrainPod: Training results
